{
  "stem": "7546.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Now picture this inhumanity by men, and your blood curdles.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And this you saw with your own eyes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It's not something that someone told you, because all the able men and women that were going to work had to be downstairs in the yard, and being examined by the Germans, if they're able to work or not.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Just like my wife's mother was not able to work, but she was in the line-up.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She thought maybe she's going to pass the inspection, but she didn't.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I passed inspection.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "My wife passed the inspection.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We were still able.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We had a little life in us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We could work and do something for them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But to see the children flying through the windows into the trucks with their blood splattered all over the truck, and around the truck, and on the ground, that was something that is really not for a human mind to comprehend.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It certainly was not for my mind to comprehend.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I couldn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And that went on and on and on for about two weeks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And when we heard the word of a Shpero, that a Shpero is coming, our blood curdles.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Our blood became ice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And on about the 22nd or 23rd of May, the same year of 1942, new transports used to come in from western Europe-- from Austria, Czechoslovakia, western Germany-- all of Germany.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They used to come in to the Lodz ghetto to replenish the people that-- that were taken.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I think, if I remember correctly, it was about 35,000 or 40,000 people that were taken away in 1942.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And about 20,000 came back from Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
